description:
BEYOND the DARKNESS sees Identified Flying Objects: A Multidisciplinary Scientific Approach to the UFO Phenomenon with Dr. Michael Masters.

Could "aliens" simply be us, but from the future?

Using an academic approach firmly rooted in Anthropology, Astronomy, Astrobiology, and Physics, Dr. Michael P. Masters, author of Identified Flying Objects: A Multidisciplinary Scientific Approach to the UFO Phenomenon, explores the premise that "UFOs" & "Aliens," if real, are our distant human descendants, who are returning from the future to study us as members of their own hominin evolutionary past.
